                     <title xml:lang="fa">مرآت احمدي</title>
                     <note>Folio one, recto: two impressions of small bevelled rectangular seal: David Pris 1210. Last back flyleaf, verso: When kindred souls shall blend in [one?] another. Red leather Oriental bind with blind stamped and tooled decoration. Spine a European replacement. Detached portions of the work, as described in Morley's printed catalogue. Parts of the same work as Codrington/Reade No 82. Space for rubrics left unfilled.</note>
